《'''新消息报'''》是一份在以色列特拉维夫出版的全国性日报。《新消息报》于1939年在英属巴勒斯坦成立，是以色列销量和发行量最大的报纸。<ref name="news.bbc.co.uk">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/4969714.stm |title=The press in Israel |date=May 8, 2006 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |access-date=April 25, 2019 |archive-date=2012-07-17 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120717083025/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/4969714.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=jvl>[http://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Society_&_Culture/press.html The Israeli Press] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Society_%26_Culture/press.html |date=20020911024443 }} Jewish Virtual Library</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapid=8032790 |title=Yedioth Aharonot Group: Private Company Information - Businessweek |publisher=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]] |access-date=April 25, 2019 |archive-date=2019-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190224173555/https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapid=8032790 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
== 历史 ==
[[File:Yediot.jpg|thumb]]http://nadlan.walla.co.il/item/2945873 {{Wayback|url=http://nadlan.walla.co.il/item/2945873 |date=20210121000443 }}</ref>]]
《新消息报》于1939年由一位名叫格肖姆·科马罗夫的投资者建立。它是英国托管巴勒斯坦地区的第一份晚报，并试图模仿伦敦《旗帜晚报》的形式。由于遇到了财政困难，科马罗夫把报纸卖给了叶胡达·莫泽斯。莫泽斯是一位富有的土地商人，他把这份报纸视为一种有趣的爱好和长期的金融投资。他的两个儿子鲁本和诺亚掌管着这份报纸，诺亚是该报的首任执行主编。<ref name="jvl"/>
